The '''Davao del Norte Football Association''' is a provincial football association under the [[Philippine Football Federation]] (PFF) which serves [[Davao del Norte]] area. As of 2015, it is led by president Renato Cosmod who is also simultaneously serving as Vice President of the PFF.<ref>{{cite news|title=PH football on crossroad|url=http://www.pinoyfootball.com/articles/11101714/PH-football-on-crossroad|accessdate=13 August 2015|publisher=Pinoyfootball.com|date=11 August 2015}}</ref> The Davao del Norte F.A. sends a team to represent the region in the yearly [[PFF National Men's Club Championship]].
