{{Infobox stadium | name = Estadio Chihuahua | fullname = Estadio Monumental Chihuahua | image = Chihuahua stadium 2008.jpg | caption = Estadio Chihuahua night game 2009 | location = [[Chihuahua, Chihuahua|Chihuahua]], [[Chihuahua (state)|Chihuahua]], [[Mexico]] | coordinates = {{coord|28|37|33|N|106|1|20|W|type:landmark|display=it}} | opened = 13 August 2004<ref name="world_stadiums"/> | capacity = 14,500<ref name="world_stadiums">{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/north_america/countries/mexico/northern_mexico.shtml|title=World Stadiums - Stadiums in Mexico :: Northern Mexico|accessdate=2011-06-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605142819/http://www.worldstadiums.com/north_america/countries/mexico/northern_mexico.shtml|archivedate=2011-06-05|df=}}</ref> | tenants = [[Dorados de Chihuahua]] }} '''Estadio Chihuahua''' is a [[stadium]] in [[Chihuahua, Chihuahua|Chihuahua]], [[Mexico]]. It is primarily used for [[baseball]], and is the home field of the [[Dorados de Chihuahua]] baseball team of the [[Liga Mexicana de Beisbol|Mexican League]].<ref>[http://www.oem.com.mx/esto/notas/n983161.htm ''Dorados de Chihuahua de Beisbol''. Esto.]</ref> It holds 14,500 people and opened in 2005.<ref name="world_stadiums"/>
