{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2014}} {{Unreferenced|date= November 2014}} {{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Gradski Stadion | nickname = | image = | fullname = | location = [[Prijedor]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | built = | opened = | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = [[FK Rudar Prijedor]] | operator = [[FK Rudar Prijedor]] | surface = | construction_cost = | architect = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor= | project_manager = | main_contractors = | former_names = | tenants = [[FK Rudar Prijedor]] | seating_capacity = 6,000 | dimensions = }}
'''Gradski stadion in Prijedor''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Prijedor]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[FK Rudar Prijedor|FK Rudar]]. The stadium can seat 2,000.
