{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Kremin Stadium | nickname = | image = Kremenchuk Kremin-Arena 1.jpg | location = [[Kremenchuk]], [[Ukraine]] | coordinates = {{coord|47.5167|N|36.4833|E}} | broke_ground = | opened = November 2010 | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = [[Kremenchuk]] | operator = | surface = Artficial | construction_cost = [[Ukrainian hryvnia|₴]] 2,500,000<ref>[http://fckremin.com.ua/news/2007/06/15/vlasnij_stadion_mati_89.html Oфiцiйний сайт ФК «Кремінь» Кременчук<!-- Bot generated title -->]{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> | architect = | former_names = | tenants = [[FC Kremin Kremenchuk|MFC Kremin Kremenchuk]] | seating_capacity = 1,500 ([[football (soccer)|football]]) | dimensions = 105m x 68m }}
'''Kremin Stadium''' ({{lang-uk|Стадіон «Кремінь»}}) is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Kremenchuk]], [[Ukraine]].<ref>[http://www.kremenchug-ua.com/other/viewnews.php?id=249&d=26.09.2007 Kremenchug-ua.com » Подробное описание новости на 26.09.2007<!-- Bot generated title -->]{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> The stadium is a home arena for [[FC Kremin Kremenchuk]].
Having an artificial, in the summer of 2017 the stadium was accepted by the Professional Football League to host games of the [[Ukrainian First League]].<ref>[https://www.telegraf.in.ua/kremenchug/2017/06/22/dolya-stadonu-kremn-arena-sche-virshuyetsya_10062662.html Decision about the Kremin-Arena Stadium was adopted (Рішення по стадіону «Кремінь-Арена» прийняли )]. Telegraf. 22 June 2017</ref>
