The '''Memorial Cimurri''' (also called '''Gran Premio Bioera''') is a late season [[road bicycle race]] held annually near [[Reggio Emilia]], in the region of [[Emilia Romagna]], [[Italy]]. Since 2005, the race has been organised as a [[1.1]] event on the [[UCI Europe Tour]].

