{{Notability|Biographies|date=October 2010}}
'''Ronan Flood''' has been the [[caddie]] of [[professional golfer]] [[Pádraig Harrington]] since 2004.  He is a former assistant bank manager for [[Allied Irish Banks|AIB]] and played to a two [[handicap (golf)|handicap]]. He and Harrington have been close friends since childhood and are married to sisters Caroline and Suzie Gregan.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.ie/sport/golf/partners-in-the-sublime-1441789.html |title=Partners in the sublime |newspaper=[[Irish Independent]] |first=Dermot |last=Gilleece |date=27 July 2008 |accessdate=2010-06-28}}</ref>

